    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群（日常讨论，欢迎加入！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建武：708047871 （推荐） Bug反馈：745684470</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元鼎：721692702（已满）；开皇：790057337（已满）；始元：515177519（已满） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >元光：763994907（已满）；建元：348526869（已满）；贞观：660323700（已满）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/a25e6e7f38e674eff8752a1ff5d06e6e.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/3fed4c17d3b822c693697db1cbc9a8b9.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=256 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎试玩0.24测试版，现阶段仍会有不少BUG和不平衡之处有待发现和优化，欢迎反馈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >计划收费的0.3抢先体验版即将到来，希望可以在近期上线，<strong>欢迎大家前往抢先体验版的商店页面将游戏添加入愿望单↑</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《皇帝与社稷》是一款融合了策略、经营、养成、收集等玩法的皇帝模拟游戏。玩家将扮演古代的君主，治理国家、收集历代名臣妃子、培育后代，最终通过世代传承，建设一个长盛不衰的帝国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/11e56a6792470ea5f0fb1b8fd6f9b225.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=134 /></span>上朝理政，处理奏章，设定国家政策。国家社稷包含超过20种不同属性，它们之间互相依存、互相影响。通过梳理和调整各种属性之间的关系来使国家稳定健康的发展壮大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/509a71742a9156b499e7c24fa9170628.poster.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/509a71742a9156b499e7c24fa9170628.webm?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/509a71742a9156b499e7c24fa9170628.mp4?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >颁布诏命，思考拟策，指派官员，执行政令。政令分为七大类，需要在吏，户，礼，兵，刑，工六部尚书和丞相处下达。通过这些政令来实现对国家的统治和发展，多数政令需要皇帝和大臣通过拟策来合作完成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/92d1c80d0b15cf4f7afa72c03b5db2f3.poster.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/92d1c80d0b15cf4f7afa72c03b5db2f3.webm?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/92d1c80d0b15cf4f7afa72c03b5db2f3.mp4?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纵横捭阖，远交近攻，游刃于诸邦。向他国派遣使者、建立贸易关系，亦或是发动战争……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/b9a52737b332be95480b2b76383862ba.poster.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/b9a52737b332be95480b2b76383862ba.webm?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/b9a52737b332be95480b2b76383862ba.mp4?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >训练士兵，筹备军需。待时机成熟，攻城略地。通过发布军事指令影响战争走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/884cd2d3e8d061d85e10dab89f7d3f13.poster.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/884cd2d3e8d061d85e10dab89f7d3f13.webm?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/884cd2d3e8d061d85e10dab89f7d3f13.mp4?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/8b5e2759dcb69b80da277b5772c12d17.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=134 /></span>发展教育，促进科举，搜罗王佐之臣。通过每年一次的秋试与额外的制举，收集能力出众的历史名臣，并因材施用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/6472eb6ce1e95afb3e1c257cf35ac76e.poster.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/6472eb6ce1e95afb3e1c257cf35ac76e.webm?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/6472eb6ce1e95afb3e1c257cf35ac76e.mp4?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/7eb1127ba4b22d22906552eb609792bd.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=134 /></span>皇帝具有理政，仁德，勇健，才艺四项属性，在皇宫中的各种设施中历练即可提升对应属性。皇帝自身属性会极大影响治国效率，合理安排每日时间，锻炼自我。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/420be553c5324544299afe9dd63a4051.poster.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/420be553c5324544299afe9dd63a4051.webm?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/420be553c5324544299afe9dd63a4051.mp4?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/2d79be74acb7fa979ee4cfe4295d4066.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=134 /></span>收罗天下粉黛，六宫藏娇，享尽世间荣华。在后宫册封嫔妃，繁衍皇嗣，也可以在此处放松心情，从而提高做其他事的效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/9e6c61410a529b8664ad0e27e42a9c61.poster.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/9e6c61410a529b8664ad0e27e42a9c61.webm?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/9e6c61410a529b8664ad0e27e42a9c61.mp4?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/999c72e4ebfa6ef6b8248b24a04c5101.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=134 /></span>皇帝也是肉体凡胎，寿元终有耗尽之日。提前挑选资质最佳的皇子，对其进行重点培育。在现任皇帝驾崩后，皇嗣会继任皇位，游戏也将继续进行！经过一代又一代的传承，打造属于你的永世帝国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/8df8772932d67e49f9b82a86251fefbf.poster.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/8df8772932d67e49f9b82a86251fefbf.webm?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/8df8772932d67e49f9b82a86251fefbf.mp4?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/1c82795c1390555e84d1c4f9fb4fd487.poster.avif?t=1745907238\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/1c82795c1390555e84d1c4f9fb4fd487.webm?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729700/extras/1c82795c1390555e84d1c4f9fb4fd487.mp4?t=1745907238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一点释疑</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或许您现在脑海中浮现出的是DOS时代的那一抹回忆，或许想到的是其他类似题材的手游，质疑这又是个换皮加抄袭的垃圾游戏，其实吧~还真是挺像，无非也是“吏户礼兵刑工”六部机构，前朝发展，宫中历练的总框架，因为，这个框架本就是最合理的，DOS《皇帝》能被大家认可，甚至被奉为经典三十余年仍有余晖，这也是核心原因所在。所以《皇帝与社稷》无法摒弃这一经典框架，而在传承先辈框架下又想表达些不同的东西：泱泱华夏有两千余年封建史，各种阶层的对立关系贯穿其间，譬如：君与臣，君与党，国与民，士与庶，国与国，后宫与前朝。作为一国之君，必须要面对这些矛盾，做出调整和决策。这也是皇帝这个职业最与众不同，且技术含量的精华所在，这就是《皇帝与社稷》这款游戏的创作初衷。希望通过游戏，去还原这种感觉，就是制衡之道！《皇帝与社稷》最终要做成游戏中的各项数值都不是孤立的，不是简单地数据堆积实现增长，然后成为强国四处征战，而是在发展过程中会出现种种矛盾关系，皇帝需要做出取舍。比如为什么在很多情况下皇帝知道对方是佞臣，却依然重用？为什么有时皇帝明知是忠臣而不得不杀？为何皇帝引用外戚势力很容易引发专权而历史上又屡见不鲜？……这些偏硬核的内容，都是我想要实现的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关于版本</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，愿景谈何容易...刚才那只是个大饼，我凭一己之力埋头三年，目前的进度其实是完成了大的框架和基本功能，在多年以前我是游戏公司里的一名3D美术，因为感到那时的工作内容并不是我想要的，流行的网游的虽然画面精美酷炫却味同嚼蜡，毅然辞职开始自学程序，拾起了十九年前的那个剧本，踏上一生都想走的那条路，随着一年又一年的过去，三十多岁没有生活的压力是不可能的谁老谁知道，赌注和负担变的越来越大，面对一些难度更大的程序部分也显得力不从心，久了以至于有点害怕了，真的害怕压力面前不得不半途而废，害怕倒在那条最豪迈的路上，再三考量之后，我还是决定对目前所做的基本功能进行收尾，发布这个0.1测试版，这对我个人来说其实意义重大：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.我需要大家的反馈，反馈这个题材和制作方向是否还有人在意；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.帮助我对目前版本做个数据平衡方面的矫正，和后期游戏机制上的取舍；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.后边有高级些的代码部分我不得不要找更专业的程序来帮助完成，开销较大，走这一步需要勇气和信心给自己，给家人；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关乎去留，我很在意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于在发布之前都是我一个人在测试，精力有限，必定不乏疏漏，初代版本如果觉得有不好的地方或BUG，请多包涵，大家的一切评价我都接受，我会努力更新，优化，完善的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外要特别说明的是测试版只会更新到0.2+版，从0.3版开始是不断完善的正式版，需要另外购买。</p>",
